    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="postcard">
                <pb facs="#Michele_prima"/>
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date>1-6-1916</date>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>
                    	<presentation>
                        	<recipient>Mrs. Boscelli Celeste via Antonio Stoppani n 7 Lambrate Milan</recipient>
                        	<address><persName ref="Creator">Michele villa</persName>, Private, Reg 112, Company 11</address>
                        	Dear sister <persName ref="Celeste_Boscelli">Celeste</persName>
                    	</presentation>
                    </salute>
                </opener>
                <p>     
                	I am in good health and so I hope for you and your dear husband and family. I received your dear letter on the 31st and I answer with my news saying that I am near 
                    <placeName ref="Cittadella">Cittadella</placeName> in the province of <placeName ref="Padova">Padova</placeName> to go on the Trentino front but I don’t know the position, 
                    I hope that it will be better than where I was it was very dangerous.
                    For now I salute you with all my heart and my salutes to <persName ref="Luigi_Bosetta">Luigi Bosetta</persName> and <persName ref="Angelo">Angelo</persName>.
                </p>
                <closer>
                    Goodbye Sincere Goodbyes a thousand kisses and salutes your brother <persName ref="Creator">Michele</persName> that always remembers you I hope to see you soon.
                    <signed></signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
